hi, i don't really know wut i'm thinkin right now...i'm kind of feeling a whole bunch of things at once...mad, sad, scared, tired, happy, excited, nervous...i could go on. i'm not gonna get into details on why i feel this way cuz it would be too hard to explain.......but anywayzzzz today i went to school, and then i came home and i was supposed to babysit but the lady called me and said she was sick so she wasn't gonna go. so now i dont have to babysit. that makes me happy. but i have a geometry test tomorrow and i'm freakin about that cuz i really really really NEED to get an A on it. i dont think i've ever gotten an A on a geometry test. but i'm gonna be dead if i dont...:( help! well anywayz, i'm gonna get goin...i luv all u guys and i love you jay...<<always
